Hark ! Father's tread ! It being now past midnight , the bird of prey went straight to roost . 
At mid day following he reappeared at the Six Jolly Fellowship Porters , in the character , not new to him , of a witness before a Coroner's Jury . 
Mr Inspector watched the proceedings too , and kept his watching closely to himself . 
