There is another ? 'There is just one other , and no more . 
Make me as compact a little will as can be reconciled with tightness , leaving the whole of the property to my beloved wife , Henerietty Boffin , sole executrix . 
Make it as short as you can , using those words but make it tight . 
At some loss to fathom Mr Boffin's notions of a tight will , Lightwood felt his way . 
'I beg your pardon , but professional profundity must be exact . 
When you say tight 'I mean tight , Mr Boffin explained . 
And nothing can be more laudable . 
But is the tightness to bind Mrs Boffin to any and what conditions ? 'Bind Mrs Boffin ? interposed her husband . 
'No ! What are you thinking of ! What I want is , to make it all hers so tight as that her hold of it can't be loosed . 
