As it got to be flood tide , and the water came nearer to them , noises on the river became more frequent , and they listened more . 
At this time of their watch , the water close to them would be often agitated by some impulsion given it from a distance . 
As the time so passed , this slinking business became a more and more precarious one . 
No one had passed in or out , since the daughter thought she heard the father calling . 
No one could pass in or out without being seen . 
