Chapter TWO NEW SERVANTS Mr and Mrs Boffin sat after breakfast , in the Bower , a prey to prosperity . 
Mr Boffin's face denoted Care and Complication . 
It is curious to consider , in such a case as Mr Boffin's , what a cheap article ink is , and how far it may be made to go . 
'Who's that , I wonder ! said Mrs Boffin . 
'Oh ! said Mr Boffin . 
