It was a stab that the blood followed , in its rush to Bradley Headstone's face , as swiftly as if it had been dealt with a dagger . 
'What do you mean by that ? was as much as he could utter . 
'A natural ambition enough , said Eugene , coolly . 
Far be it from me to say otherwise . 
