Mr Boffin heard of you through a certain Mr Lightwood . 
I think you know Mr Lightwood , or know of him ? 'I know as much of him as I wish to know , sir . 
I have no acquaintance with Mr Lightwood , and I desire none . 
I have no objection to Mr Lightwood , but I have a particular objection to some of Mr Lightwood's friends in short , to one of Mr Lightwood's friends . 
, when the careless and contemptuous bearing of Eugene Wrayburn rose before his mind . 
'I have no objection to mention the friend by name , he said , doggedly . 
