'Then perhaps the names cannot be put together on the authority of any representation of his ? 'Certainly not . 
I I hope you will not misunderstand me , sir . 
I I am much interested in this brother and sister , and the subject awakens very strong feelings within me . 
Very , very , strong feelings . 
With a shaking hand , Bradley took out his handkerchief and wiped his brow . 
All at once , in the midst of his turbulent emotions , Bradley stopped and seemed to challenge his look . 
How I come to be interested , I need not explain . 
You know the father's connection with the discovery of Mr Harmon's body . 
'Sir , replied Bradley , very restlessly indeed , 'I know all the circumstances of that case . 
