But be sure that well within the fascination of Mr Lammle's eye and smile sits little Georgiana . 
And be sure that close to little Georgiana , also under inspection by the same gingerous gentleman , sits Fledgeby . 
Strange that this impression so abides by Twemlow after being corrected , yet so it is . 
