Did you notice any wrinkles over my nose this evening , Pa ? Pa laughing at this , Bella gave him two or three shakes . 
'You won't laugh , sir , when you see your lovely woman turning haggard . 
You had better be prepared in time , I can tell you . 
Now , sir , we entered into a bond of confidence . 
Have you anything to impart ? 'I thought it was you who was to impart , my love . 
