I won't deduct for it I look to you to make it up handsomely by keeping the expenses down . 
Now , if you'll show a light , I'll come to your office room and dispose of a letter or two . 
Feigning to be intent on her embroidery , she sat plying her needle until her busy hand was stopped by Mrs Boffin's hand being lightly laid upon it . 
Yielding to the touch , she felt her hand carried to the good soul's lips , and felt a tear fall on it . 
