Try once more , dearest Mr Fledgeby . 
What is there you cannot do , if you will ! 'Thank you , said Fledgeby , 'you're very complimentary to say so . 
I don't mind trying him again , at your request . 
But of course I can't answer for the consequences . 
Riah is a tough subject , and when he says he'll do a thing , he'll do it . 
'Exactly so , cried Mrs Lammle , 'and when he says to you he'll wait , he'll wait . 
'O yes ! Here Mrs Lammle brought her handkerchief into play . 
Truly , truly , yes ! 'That makes all the difference , said Fledgeby . 
