Miss Lavinia was extremely affable to Mr Sampson on this special occasion , and took the opportunity of informing her sister why . 
Bella was glad to hear it . 
'George is getting on very well , said Miss Lavinia which might not have been supposed at the moment 'and I dare say we shall be married , one of these days . 
