Nothing should induce John to do it , when she asked him not to do it . 
That I sometimes think , John , I feel a little serious . 
'Are you too much alone , my darling ? 'O dear , no , John ! The time is so short that I have not a moment too much in the week . 
'Why serious , my life , then ? When serious ? 'When I laugh , I think , said Bella , laughing as she laid her head upon his shoulder . 
'You wouldn't believe , sir , that I feel serious now ? But I do . 
And she laughed again , and something glistened in her eyes . 
