What is your name ? A question more decidedly rushing at the secret he was keeping from her , could not have astounded him . 
But he kept his countenance and his secret , and answered , 'John Rokesmith , my dear . 
'Not goodest good , because you hesitate about it . 
However , as you know your Catechism fairly , so far , I'll let you off the rest . 
