You are all wrong there , though otherwise as right as can be . 
And now I am brought to a little piece of news , my dearest , that I might have told you earlier in the evening . 
I have strong reason for confidently believing that we shall never be in the receipt of a smaller income than our present income . 
'Why then , Lord bless this little wife of mine , there's a Fourthly ! exclaimed John . 
As he bent his face to hers , she raised hers to meet it , and laid her little right hand on his eyes , and kept it there . 
