Many flaunting dolls had to be gaily dressed , before the money was in the dressmaker's pocket to get mourning for Mr Dolls . 
'If my poor boy , she would say , 'had been brought up better , he might have done better . 
Not that I reproach myself . 
I hope I have no cause for that . 
'None indeed , Jenny , I am very certain . 
It cheers me to hear you say so . 
But you see it is so hard to bring up a child well , when you work , work , work , all day . 
When he was out of employment , I couldn't always keep him near me . 
He got fractious and nervous , and I was obliged to let him go into the streets . 
And he never did well in the streets , he never did well out of sight . 
How often it happens with children ! 'Too often , even in this sad sense ! thought the old man . 
'I had nothing to do but work , and so I worked . 
