You supposed me just now , to be the possessor of my father's property . 
But through any act of my father's , or by any right I have ? No. Through the munificence of Mr Boffin . 
of Mr and Mrs Boffin . 
But I shouldn't like to leave you , after all said and done , worse off in life than I found you . 
